Package mm.utilities.ObjectsConf

Class ObjectConf

  • java.lang.Object
    • mm.utilities.ObjectsConf.ObjectConf
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BallConf, BoxConf
    public class ObjectConf
extends java.lang.Object
    Configuration class representing a generic physics object. Contains the position (x, y), rotation angle, and static state.
